00:15:46.924 --> 00:15:50.424
hopefully we'll present data on those clinical trials later in the year.

278
00:15:52.644 --> 00:15:55.534
Here's another function of Ras, which probably no one in the audience is thinking

279
00:15:55.584 --> 00:15:55.814
about

