00:23:37.092 --> 00:23:38.452
progress through the clinic.

412
00:23:41.212 --> 00:23:44.992
So how do we get the compounds to bind into that pocket, which doesn't really exist

413
00:23:45.052 --> 00:23:45.312
in the

