00:23:46.272 --> 00:23:48.172
classical GDP-bound form?

415
00:23:48.992 --> 00:23:52.732
Well, the ability to do that is based on the fact that the switch one

416
00:23:52.772 --> 00:23:56.652
region, which is where the effective binding region, where

417
00:23:56.672 --> 00:23:58.692
Raf kinase is and other effectors bind.

418
00:23:59.512 --> 00:24:03.392
Switch one can flop back and forth between an open state as

