00:24:51.528 --> 00:24:55.308
exists in state one. So this is a P31 analysis of the

434
00:24:55.348 --> 00:24:57.928
gamma phosphates and the alpha and beta phosphates in Ras.

435
00:24:58.688 --> 00:25:00.548
This is in state two, the productive state.

436
00:25:00.928 --> 00:25:04.748
When we add drug, it moves to state one, which is the unproductive

437
00:25:04.808 --> 00:25:08.368
state where the switch one region is swinging out and can't interact with the

438
00:25:08.428 --> 00:25:08.948
effectors.

439
00:25:09.928 --> 00:25:13.268
And we can see this also in crystal structures, which is published in this

440
00:25:13.928 --> 00:25:17.668
paper as I described earlier on. So here we have the compound in the

441
00:25:18.188 --> 00:25:21.588
switch two pocket. Its binding pose and interactions look virtually

