00:25:25.668 --> 00:25:28.788
The difference though is that switch one is now pushed out into the

444
00:25:29.648 --> 00:25:32.688
floppy state, into the outside, in the state

445
00:25:33.828 --> 00:25:36.048
one configuration, which is not productive.

446
00:25:37.148 --> 00:25:39.568
So this is how the compound's able to bind.

447
00:25:39.588 --> 00:25:43.328
It sort of looks like it's binding to GDP, and it more or less binds in the same

448
00:25:43.448 --> 00:25:46.908
way, except the switch one pocket is now in an

449
00:25:46.988 --> 00:25:50.508
unproductive configuration, and you can read about that in this in more detail.

450
00:25:51.268 --> 00:25:54.828
So that principle allows us to find compounds that basically hit the

